goal: Create an event on June 10th at 10 AM titled "Visit to Bangkok National Museum."

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event
Select 'Event' from the menu to proceed with creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Visit to Bangkok National Museum'
Open the date and time picker to adjust the event details.
Fill in the Start date with 'Tuesday, June 10'
Fill in the Start time with '10:00 AM'.
Click the 'Save' button to finalize the event creation.

instruction.high_level: Create a calendar event for a visit to the Bangkok National Museum on June 10th at 10 AM
instruction.mid_level: Create an event on June 10th at 10 AM titled "Visit to Bangkok National Museum."
instruction.low_level: Create an event titled 'Visit to Bangkok National Museum' on June 10th, 2025 at 10 AM.
